{"key":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01|Heb|10","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Heb","chapter":10,"textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024","parserRevision":"v11","verses":[{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Heb:10:1","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Heb","bookOrder":57,"chapter":10,"verse":1,"text":"Since the law has only a shadow of the good things to come, and not the reality itself of those things, it can never perfect the worshipers by the same sacrifices they continually offer year after year.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Heb:10:2","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Heb","bookOrder":57,"chapter":10,"verse":2,"text":"Otherwise, wouldn’t they have stopped being offered, since the worshipers, purified once and for all, would no longer have any consciousness of sins?","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Heb:10:3","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Heb","bookOrder":57,"chapter":10,"verse":3,"text":"But in the sacrifices there is a reminder of sins year after year.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Heb:10:4","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Heb","bookOrder":57,"chapter":10,"verse":4,"text":"For it is impossible for the blood of bulls and goats to take away sins.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Heb:10:5","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Heb","bookOrder":57,"chapter":10,"verse":5,"text":"Therefore, as he was coming into the world, he said:","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Heb:10:6","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Heb","bookOrder":57,"chapter":10,"verse":6,"text":"You did not delight","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Heb:10:7","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Heb","bookOrder":57,"chapter":10,"verse":7,"text":"Then I said, “See —","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Heb:10:8","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Heb","bookOrder":57,"chapter":10,"verse":8,"text":"After he says above, You did not desire or delight in sacrifices and offerings, whole burnt offerings and sin offerings (which are offered according to the law ),","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Heb:10:9","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Heb","bookOrder":57,"chapter":10,"verse":9,"text":"he then says, See, I have come to do your will. He takes away the first to establish the second.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Heb:10:10","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Heb","bookOrder":57,"chapter":10,"verse":10,"text":"By this will, we have been sanctified through the offering of the body of Jesus Christ once for all time.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Heb:10:11","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Heb","bookOrder":57,"chapter":10,"verse":11,"text":"Every priest stands day after day ministering and offering the same sacrifices time after time, which can never take away sins.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Heb:10:12","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Heb","bookOrder":57,"chapter":10,"verse":12,"text":"But this man, after offering one sacrifice for sins forever, sat down at the right hand of God.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Heb:10:13","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Heb","bookOrder":57,"chapter":10,"verse":13,"text":"He is now waiting until his enemies are made his footstool.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Heb:10:14","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Heb","bookOrder":57,"chapter":10,"verse":14,"text":"For by one offering he has perfected forever those who are sanctified.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Heb:10:15","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Heb","bookOrder":57,"chapter":10,"verse":15,"text":"The Holy Spirit also testifies to us about this. For after he says:","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Heb:10:16","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Heb","bookOrder":57,"chapter":10,"verse":16,"text":"This is the covenant I will make with them the Lord says,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Heb:10:17","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Heb","bookOrder":57,"chapter":10,"verse":17,"text":"andI will never again remember","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Heb:10:18","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Heb","bookOrder":57,"chapter":10,"verse":18,"text":"Now where there is forgiveness of these, there is no longer an offering for sin.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Heb:10:19","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Heb","bookOrder":57,"chapter":10,"verse":19,"text":"Therefore, brothers and sisters, since we have boldness to enter the sanctuary through the blood of Jesus —","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Heb:10:20","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Heb","bookOrder":57,"chapter":10,"verse":20,"text":"he has inaugurated for us a new and living way through the curtain (that is, through his flesh ) —","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Heb:10:21","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Heb","bookOrder":57,"chapter":10,"verse":21,"text":"and since we have a great high priest over the house of God,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Heb:10:22","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Heb","bookOrder":57,"chapter":10,"verse":22,"text":"let us draw near with a true heart in full assurance of faith, with our hearts sprinkled clean from an evil conscience and our bodies washed in pure water.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Heb:10:23","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Heb","bookOrder":57,"chapter":10,"verse":23,"text":"Let us hold on to the confession of our hope without wavering, since he who promised is faithful.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Heb:10:24","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Heb","bookOrder":57,"chapter":10,"verse":24,"text":"And let us consider one another in order to provoke love and good works,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Heb:10:25","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Heb","bookOrder":57,"chapter":10,"verse":25,"text":"not neglecting to gather together, as some are in the habit of doing, but encouraging each other, and all the more as you see the day approaching.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Heb:10:26","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Heb","bookOrder":57,"chapter":10,"verse":26,"text":"For if we deliberately go on sinning after receiving the knowledge of the truth, there no longer remains a sacrifice for sins,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Heb:10:27","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Heb","bookOrder":57,"chapter":10,"verse":27,"text":"but a terrifying expectation of judgment and the fury of a fire about to consume the adversaries.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Heb:10:28","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Heb","bookOrder":57,"chapter":10,"verse":28,"text":"Anyone who disregarded the law of Moses died without mercy, based on the testimony of two or three witnesses.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Heb:10:29","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Heb","bookOrder":57,"chapter":10,"verse":29,"text":"How much worse punishment do you think one will deserve who has trampled on the Son of God, who has regarded as profane the blood of the covenant by which he was sanctified, and who has insulted the Spirit of grace?","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Heb:10:30","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Heb","bookOrder":57,"chapter":10,"verse":30,"text":"For we know the one who has said, and again,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Heb:10:31","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Heb","bookOrder":57,"chapter":10,"verse":31,"text":"It is a terrifying thing to fall into the hands of the living God.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Heb:10:32","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Heb","bookOrder":57,"chapter":10,"verse":32,"text":"Remember the earlier days when, after you had been enlightened, you endured a hard struggle with sufferings.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Heb:10:33","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Heb","bookOrder":57,"chapter":10,"verse":33,"text":"Sometimes you were publicly exposed to taunts and afflictions, and at other times you were companions of those who were treated that way.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Heb:10:34","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Heb","bookOrder":57,"chapter":10,"verse":34,"text":"For you sympathized with the prisoners and accepted with joy the confiscation of your possessions, because you know that you yourselves have a better and enduring possession.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Heb:10:35","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Heb","bookOrder":57,"chapter":10,"verse":35,"text":"So don’t throw away your confidence, which has a great reward.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Heb:10:36","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Heb","bookOrder":57,"chapter":10,"verse":36,"text":"For you need endurance, so that after you have done God’s will, you may receive what was promised.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Heb:10:37","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Heb","bookOrder":57,"chapter":10,"verse":37,"text":"For yet in a very little while,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Heb:10:38","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Heb","bookOrder":57,"chapter":10,"verse":38,"text":"But my righteous one will live by faith;","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Heb:10:39","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Heb","bookOrder":57,"chapter":10,"verse":39,"text":"But we are not those who draw back and are destroyed, but those who have faith and are saved.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"}],"layout":{"bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Heb","chapter":10,"paragraphStarts":[1,5,6,7,8,11,16,17,18,19,26,31,32,37,38,39],"headings":[{"beforeVerse":1,"text":"The Perfect Sacrifice"},{"beforeVerse":19,"text":"Exhortations to Godliness"},{"beforeVerse":26,"text":"Warning against Deliberate Sin"}],"poetryBlocks":[],"studyByVerse":[{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Heb:10:1","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Since the law has only a shadow of the good things "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Col 2:17","book":"Col","chapter":2,"verse":17,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Heb 8:5","book":"Heb","chapter":8,"verse":5,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Heb 9:11","book":"Heb","chapter":9,"verse":11,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" to come, and not the reality itself of those things, it can never perfect the worshipers by the same sacrifices they continually offer year after year. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Col 2:17","book":"Col","chapter":2,"verse":17},{"label":"Heb 8:5","book":"Heb","chapter":8,"verse":5},{"label":"Heb 9:11","book":"Heb","chapter":9,"verse":11}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Heb:10:2","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Otherwise, wouldn’t they have stopped being offered, since the worshipers, purified once and for all, would no longer have any consciousness of sins? "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Heb:10:3","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"But in the sacrifices there is a reminder of sins year after year. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Heb:10:4","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"For it is impossible for the blood of bulls and goats to take away sins."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Heb:10:5","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Therefore, as he was coming into the world, he said:"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Heb:10:6","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"You did not delight"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Heb:10:7","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Then I said, “See —"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Heb:10:8","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"After he says above, You did not desire or delight in sacrifices and offerings, whole burnt offerings and sin offerings (which are offered according to the law "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mk 12:33","book":"Mrk","chapter":12,"verse":33,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Heb 10:5–6","book":"Heb","chapter":10,"verse":5,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":"), "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mk 12:33","book":"Mrk","chapter":12,"verse":33},{"label":"Heb 10:5–6","book":"Heb","chapter":10,"verse":5}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Heb:10:9","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"he then says, See, I have come to do your will."},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Other mss add God"},{"kind":"text","text":" He takes away the first to establish the second. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Other mss add God"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Heb:10:10","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"By this will, we have been sanctified through the offering of the body of Jesus Christ once for all time. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 17:19","book":"Jhn","chapter":17,"verse":19,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Heb 7:27","book":"Heb","chapter":7,"verse":27,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Heb 9:12","book":"Heb","chapter":9,"verse":12,"letter":"c"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Jn 17:19","book":"Jhn","chapter":17,"verse":19},{"label":"Heb 7:27","book":"Heb","chapter":7,"verse":27},{"label":"Heb 9:12","book":"Heb","chapter":9,"verse":12}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Heb:10:11","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Every priest stands day after day ministering and offering the same sacrifices time after time, which can never take away sins. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Nm 28:3","book":"Num","chapter":28,"verse":3,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Heb 5:1","book":"Heb","chapter":5,"verse":1,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Nm 28:3","book":"Num","chapter":28,"verse":3},{"label":"Heb 5:1","book":"Heb","chapter":5,"verse":1}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Heb:10:12","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"But this man, after offering one sacrifice for sins forever, sat down at the right hand of God. "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Or offering one sacrifice for sins, sat down forever at the right hand of God"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 8:34","book":"Rom","chapter":8,"verse":34,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Eph 1:20","book":"Eph","chapter":1,"verse":20,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Col 3:1","book":"Col","chapter":3,"verse":1,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Heb 1:3","book":"Heb","chapter":1,"verse":3,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Heb 8:1","book":"Heb","chapter":8,"verse":1,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Heb 12:2","book":"Heb","chapter":12,"verse":2,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Pt 3:22","book":"1Pe","chapter":3,"verse":22,"letter":"g"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Rm 8:34","book":"Rom","chapter":8,"verse":34},{"label":"Eph 1:20","book":"Eph","chapter":1,"verse":20},{"label":"Col 3:1","book":"Col","chapter":3,"verse":1},{"label":"Heb 1:3","book":"Heb","chapter":1,"verse":3},{"label":"Heb 8:1","book":"Heb","chapter":8,"verse":1},{"label":"Heb 12:2","book":"Heb","chapter":12,"verse":2},{"label":"1Pt 3:22","book":"1Pe","chapter":3,"verse":22}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Or offering one sacrifice for sins, sat down forever at the right hand of God"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Heb:10:13","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"He is now waiting until his enemies are made his footstool. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ps 110:1","book":"Psa","chapter":110,"verse":1,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 22:44","book":"Mat","chapter":22,"verse":44,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mk 12:36","book":"Mrk","chapter":12,"verse":36,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 20:43","book":"Luk","chapter":20,"verse":43,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 2:34–35","book":"Act","chapter":2,"verse":34,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 15:25","book":"1Co","chapter":15,"verse":25,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Heb 1:13","book":"Heb","chapter":1,"verse":13,"letter":"g"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ps 110:1","book":"Psa","chapter":110,"verse":1},{"label":"Mt 22:44","book":"Mat","chapter":22,"verse":44},{"label":"Mk 12:36","book":"Mrk","chapter":12,"verse":36},{"label":"Lk 20:43","book":"Luk","chapter":20,"verse":43},{"label":"Ac 2:34–35","book":"Act","chapter":2,"verse":34},{"label":"1Co 15:25","book":"1Co","chapter":15,"verse":25},{"label":"Heb 1:13","book":"Heb","chapter":1,"verse":13}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Heb:10:14","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"For by one offering he has perfected forever those who are sanctified. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Heb:10:15","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"The Holy Spirit also testifies to us about this. For after he says:"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Heb:10:16","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"This is the covenant I will make with them"},{"kind":"text","text":" the Lord says,"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Heb:10:17","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"andI will never again remember"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Heb:10:18","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Now where there is forgiveness of these, there is no longer an offering for sin."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Heb:10:19","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Therefore, brothers and sisters, since we have boldness to enter the sanctuary through the blood of Jesus "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Eph 2:18","book":"Eph","chapter":2,"verse":18,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Heb 9:25","book":"Heb","chapter":9,"verse":25,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" — "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Eph 2:18","book":"Eph","chapter":2,"verse":18},{"label":"Heb 9:25","book":"Heb","chapter":9,"verse":25}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Heb:10:20","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"he has inaugurated "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Or opened"},{"kind":"text","text":" for us a new and living way through the curtain (that is, through his flesh "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 10:9","book":"Jhn","chapter":10,"verse":9,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Heb 9:3","book":"Heb","chapter":9,"verse":3,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Heb 9:8","book":"Heb","chapter":9,"verse":8,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":") — "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Jn 10:9","book":"Jhn","chapter":10,"verse":9},{"label":"Heb 9:3","book":"Heb","chapter":9,"verse":3},{"label":"Heb 9:8","book":"Heb","chapter":9,"verse":8}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Or opened"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Heb:10:21","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"and since we have a great high priest over the house of God, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Heb 2:17","book":"Heb","chapter":2,"verse":17,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Heb 4:14","book":"Heb","chapter":4,"verse":14,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Heb 2:17","book":"Heb","chapter":2,"verse":17},{"label":"Heb 4:14","book":"Heb","chapter":4,"verse":14}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Heb:10:22","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"let us draw near with a true heart in full assurance of faith, with our hearts sprinkled clean from an evil conscience and our bodies washed in pure water. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ezk 36:25","book":"Ezk","chapter":36,"verse":25,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Heb 9:14","book":"Heb","chapter":9,"verse":14,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ezk 36:25","book":"Ezk","chapter":36,"verse":25},{"label":"Heb 9:14","book":"Heb","chapter":9,"verse":14}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Heb:10:23","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Let us hold on to the confession of our hope without wavering, since he who promised is faithful. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 1:9","book":"1Co","chapter":1,"verse":9,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Heb 3:6","book":"Heb","chapter":3,"verse":6,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"1Co 1:9","book":"1Co","chapter":1,"verse":9},{"label":"Heb 3:6","book":"Heb","chapter":3,"verse":6}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Heb:10:24","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"And let us consider one another in order to provoke love and good works, "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Heb:10:25","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"not neglecting to gather together, as some are in the habit of doing, but encouraging each other, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 2:42","book":"Act","chapter":2,"verse":42,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 13:11","book":"Rom","chapter":13,"verse":11,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Heb 3:13","book":"Heb","chapter":3,"verse":13,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" and all the more as you see the day approaching."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ac 2:42","book":"Act","chapter":2,"verse":42},{"label":"Rm 13:11","book":"Rom","chapter":13,"verse":11},{"label":"Heb 3:13","book":"Heb","chapter":3,"verse":13}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Heb:10:26","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"For if we deliberately go on sinning after receiving the knowledge of the truth, there no longer remains a sacrifice for sins, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Nm 15:30","book":"Num","chapter":15,"verse":30,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dt 17:12","book":"Deu","chapter":17,"verse":12,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Heb 6:4","book":"Heb","chapter":6,"verse":4,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Pt 2:20","book":"2Pe","chapter":2,"verse":20,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Jn 5:16","book":"1Jn","chapter":5,"verse":16,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Nm 15:30","book":"Num","chapter":15,"verse":30},{"label":"Dt 17:12","book":"Deu","chapter":17,"verse":12},{"label":"Heb 6:4","book":"Heb","chapter":6,"verse":4},{"label":"2Pt 2:20","book":"2Pe","chapter":2,"verse":20},{"label":"1Jn 5:16","book":"1Jn","chapter":5,"verse":16}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Heb:10:27","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"but a terrifying expectation of judgment and the fury of a fire about to consume the adversaries. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 26:11","book":"Isa","chapter":26,"verse":11,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Zp 1:18","book":"Zep","chapter":1,"verse":18,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Th 1:8","book":"2Th","chapter":1,"verse":8,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Is 26:11","book":"Isa","chapter":26,"verse":11},{"label":"Zp 1:18","book":"Zep","chapter":1,"verse":18},{"label":"2Th 1:8","book":"2Th","chapter":1,"verse":8}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Heb:10:28","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Anyone who disregarded the law of Moses died without mercy, based on the testimony of two or three witnesses. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dt 17:6","book":"Deu","chapter":17,"verse":6,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Heb 2:2","book":"Heb","chapter":2,"verse":2,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Dt 17:6","book":"Deu","chapter":17,"verse":6},{"label":"Heb 2:2","book":"Heb","chapter":2,"verse":2}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Heb:10:29","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"How much worse punishment do you think one will deserve who has trampled on the Son of God, who has regarded as profane "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Or ordinary"},{"kind":"text","text":" the blood of the covenant by which he was sanctified, and who has insulted the Spirit of grace? "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 12:31–32","book":"Mat","chapter":12,"verse":31,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Eph 4:30","book":"Eph","chapter":4,"verse":30,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Heb 6:6","book":"Heb","chapter":6,"verse":6,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mt 12:31–32","book":"Mat","chapter":12,"verse":31},{"label":"Eph 4:30","book":"Eph","chapter":4,"verse":30},{"label":"Heb 6:6","book":"Heb","chapter":6,"verse":6}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Or ordinary"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Heb:10:30","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"For we know the one who has said,"},{"kind":"text","text":" and again,"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Heb:10:31","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"It is a terrifying thing to fall into the hands of the living God. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 16:16","book":"Mat","chapter":16,"verse":16,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 12:5","book":"Luk","chapter":12,"verse":5,"letter":"b"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mt 16:16","book":"Mat","chapter":16,"verse":16},{"label":"Lk 12:5","book":"Luk","chapter":12,"verse":5}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Heb:10:32","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Remember the earlier days when, after you had been enlightened, you endured a hard struggle with sufferings. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Php 1:29–30","book":"Php","chapter":1,"verse":29,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Heb 6:4","book":"Heb","chapter":6,"verse":4,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Php 1:29–30","book":"Php","chapter":1,"verse":29},{"label":"Heb 6:4","book":"Heb","chapter":6,"verse":4}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Heb:10:33","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Sometimes you were publicly exposed to taunts and afflictions, and at other times you were companions of those who were treated that way. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 4:9","book":"1Co","chapter":4,"verse":9,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Php 4:14","book":"Php","chapter":4,"verse":14,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Th 2:14","book":"1Th","chapter":2,"verse":14,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"1Co 4:9","book":"1Co","chapter":4,"verse":9},{"label":"Php 4:14","book":"Php","chapter":4,"verse":14},{"label":"1Th 2:14","book":"1Th","chapter":2,"verse":14}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Heb:10:34","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"For you sympathized with the prisoners "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Other mss read sympathized with my imprisonment"},{"kind":"text","text":" and accepted with joy the confiscation of your possessions, because you know that you yourselves have a better and enduring possession. "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":2,"text":"Other mss add in heaven"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 5:12","book":"Mat","chapter":5,"verse":12,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Pt 1:4","book":"1Pe","chapter":1,"verse":4,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mt 5:12","book":"Mat","chapter":5,"verse":12},{"label":"1Pt 1:4","book":"1Pe","chapter":1,"verse":4}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Other mss read sympathized with my imprisonment"},{"marker":2,"text":"Other mss add in heaven"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Heb:10:35","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"So don’t throw away your confidence, which has a great reward. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Heb 2:2","book":"Heb","chapter":2,"verse":2,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Heb 11:26","book":"Heb","chapter":11,"verse":26,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Heb 2:2","book":"Heb","chapter":2,"verse":2},{"label":"Heb 11:26","book":"Heb","chapter":11,"verse":26}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Heb:10:36","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"For you need endurance, so that after you have done God’s will, you may receive what was promised. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 21:19","book":"Luk","chapter":21,"verse":19,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Heb 12:1","book":"Heb","chapter":12,"verse":1,"letter":"b"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Lk 21:19","book":"Luk","chapter":21,"verse":19},{"label":"Heb 12:1","book":"Heb","chapter":12,"verse":1}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Heb:10:37","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"For yet in a very little while,"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Heb:10:38","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"But my righteous one"},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Other mss read the righteous one"},{"kind":"text","text":" will live by faith;"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Other mss read the righteous one"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Heb:10:39","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"But we are not those who draw back and are destroyed, but those who have faith and are saved."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]}]},"cachedAt":1783279680379}